    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! It drives smoothly, looks great, and has plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
