    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the premium seating surfaces remain supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, including a recent comprehensive inspection, fresh fluids, and a newer set of all-season tires. On the road, it performs beautifully with smooth gear transitions and a quiet, composed suspension. This is a solid, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
