    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
